Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.75,0:00:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang jual takoyaki di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.59,0:00:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang! Beli takoyakinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.71,0:00:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dua takoyaki mentaiko mayo pedas\Nyang warnanya kayak rambut Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.84,0:00:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siap.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkat semua pengalaman\Nkonyol sebelumnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.89,0:00:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akhirnya bisa tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.60,0:00:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}F/ACE bakal mampir ke sekolah kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.14,0:00:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Idola favoritku muncul di sekolah
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}persis seperti khayalanku miliaran kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.06,0:00:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak percaya ini jadi kenyataan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.81,0:00:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita masih kayak biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}SMA kami
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah markas penggemar berat F/ACE.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.91,0:02:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanti pasti bakal heboh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita, mau istirahat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.46,0:02:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke, sisanya kuserahkan ke kalian, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Riko dan Yuina yang jaga stan klub.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.51,0:02:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau bagaimana lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku keliling sendiri saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.27,0:02:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini dia Festival Budaya yang legendaris.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Energinya luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Agak seram, tapi entah kenapa\Naku tak bisa berpaling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Suram!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.78,0:02:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf aku sangat menjijikkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.28,0:02:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Harusnya bilang, "Maaf aku terlalu keren."\N- Ibu, ada orang aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Maaf.\N- Shh, jangan dilihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.20,0:02:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Seragam itu...\N- Ayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau lumayan tampan pakai seragam itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suara itu Saka... Pak Gorila?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hebat juga kau mengenaliku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.09,0:03:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa auraku terlalu kuat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gorila pakai topeng gorila.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lagi senggang.\NTemani aku keliling Festival Budaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Temani berkeliling...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.48,0:03:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya lagi senggang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian tak apa-apa santai di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah harus siap-siap?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masih ada waktu sebelum tampil.\NTenang saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin promosi rumah hantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pokoknya kita harus hati-hati
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}biar tak ketahuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Utage, ternyata kau di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang di belakangmu itu\Nteman SMP-mu, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terus, yang ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.26,0:03:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Teman SMP-ku yang lain juga.\N- Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, begitu.\NSalam kenal, teman nomor dua.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan lihat-lihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melihat mereka bersenang-senang,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku jadi ikut senang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf. Kinoshita,\Nkau tidak terluka, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pegang ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.46,0:04:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahaya! Jangan sentuh itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baru pertama kali\Ndatang ke Festival Budaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.34,0:05:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sibuk kerja saat SMP dan SMA,\Njadi tak sempat ikut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}SMP-ku gelar Festival Budaya\Ntiap tiga tahun sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.72,0:05:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sialnya, aku malah kena flu di hari H.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayang banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masuk SMA, aku ikut audisi bakat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelahnya aku sibuk banget
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sampai tak bisa ikut\NFestival Budaya SMA.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya hari ini aku senang banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.82,0:05:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Senang rasanya bisa berbaur\Ndengan penggemar sebagai orang biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.04,0:05:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya ingin kulindungi ruangan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Andai aku bisa jadi udara\Ndan terus menetap di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada Keito di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kardus di kepalanya itu sama persis\Ndengan tempat sampah di kamarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah pasti itu dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, apa semua anggota F/ACE\Nmenyusup ke Festival Budaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang itu benar-benar pakai\Nkardus susu di kepalanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.97,0:05:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kelihatannya kau anggap dia lucu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tapi topeng gorila itu juga sama.\N- Ingin kuhirup ketampanan anak F/ACE.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:05:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:06:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagian, ini kan almamater Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti dia keliling buat nostalgia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tepung modal 10 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gurita, telur, saus, mayones.\NSatu porsi modalnya 100 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dijual 500 yen di sini?\NUntung besar, tuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau bikin di rumah,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}termasuk gas dan listrik.\Naku bisa hemat 300 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia meremehkan takoyaki kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa-apaan? Ternyata kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau makan bareng?\NGabung saja sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.92,0:06:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enggak, makasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terlalu mencolok kalau bergerombol.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini tisu basah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan berbuat onar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iri banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pantas saja, ternyata kau murid sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dulu aku juga\Npunya banyak kerja sambilan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekolah ini memang bolehkan\Nkerja sambilan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kafe tempat kerjamu dulu
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kini jadi spot wajib\Nbagi para penggemar Keito.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.78,0:06:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin karena\Naku paling lama kerja di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sih masih bisa ke sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi suruh mereka donasi\Nyang banyak di kanal resmi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:06:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulutmu masih pedas saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sana pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Identitas mereka tak ketahuan sama sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada yang sangka Tamon\Njalannya membungkuk begini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan jalan Ori kayak preman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.81,0:07:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu Natsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.07,0:07:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagunya sudah siap?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berkatmu, lagunya selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.66,0:07:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bantu banyak,\Ntapi aku senang mendengarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Natsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau selalu bolos latihan\Ndan malas kerja.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku muak melihatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.35,0:07:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kuakui kau memang berbakat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pokoknya, berikan yang terbaik.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.65,0:08:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sikap apa itu?\NYang lebih semangat, dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berisik.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sama sekali tak mendengarkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Natsuki sepertinya\Nsulit menghadapi Ori.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kelihatannya sih begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tapi mereka lebih akur\N- Dengar, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- daripada biasanya hari ini.\N- Coba lihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu dibilang akur?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bisa tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku panitia tunggal,\Njadi harus fokus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asu, mampirlah ke Klub Seni.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penggemar kira tinggi Natsuki cuma 15 cm.\NKhayalan yang lucu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanannya pasti gulali.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan keliling-keliling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal dia benci makanan manis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau ada kesempatan bicara,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku harus minta maaf karena\Nkasar dan bikin dia salah paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga mau minta maaf soal tempo hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.25,0:09:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya, lagi bersenang-senang?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takoyaki, pisang cokelat,\Npaduan suara, drama, rumah hantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Acaranya sudah mulai.\N- Kalian sudah mampir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu kan suara...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, ini baru pertama kali\Naku ke Festival Budaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dulu pas SMP aku tak bisa ikut\Ngara-gara flu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga kena flu, Tamon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, pastilah aku kena flu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Habisnya kau kelihatan kuat banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Masa sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke, cukup basa-basinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya, tahu siapa kami, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.12,0:09:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, siapa kami sebenarnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.33,0:09:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jawabannya ada di panggung khusus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Konsernya akan segera mulai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Semuanya, kumpul!\N- Kumpul!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo, Semuanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.47,0:10:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Halo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.48,0:10:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menikmati Festival Budayanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.98,0:10:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bakal makin seru, nih.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.19,0:10:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mohon dukungannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti kalian kaget, kan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kami tiba-tiba datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.62,0:10:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kejutan kami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sukses besar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Maaf bikin kalian kaget!\N- Berhasil!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.04,0:10:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke. Lihat kemari.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tanpa basa-basi lagi,\Nada pengumuman buat kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Pengumuman apa?\N- Apa itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.96,0:10:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulai Januari depan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}variety show perdana kami,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}F/ACE SCHOOL, akan tayang!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asyik banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.98,0:10:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di episode spesial pertamanya,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.77,0:10:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}konser hari ini bakal ditayangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ditunggu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, lagu tema acaranya\Njuga sudah ditentukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:10:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau dengar?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.78,0:11:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagu ini untuk kalian semua\Nyang sudah berjuang keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lirik dan musik oleh Natsuki Ishibashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Judulnya, "FLY".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Terbang lebih tinggi, melesat jauh
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rentangkan sayapmu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita F/ACE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada lagi yang bisa dilakukan\NKita hanya mondar-mandir - benar
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya mondar-mandir\NMenghabiskan siang dan malam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.45,0:11:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bilang "Kerja keras itu menyebalkan"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak sadar betapa bodohnya itu\NTak akan pernah
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keraguan yang egois
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:11:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak bisa melihat hal lain
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi buat apa? Kau sudah sadar\Nkebenarannya, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua kegagalan di masa lalu
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagian dari impianku\NJangan dibuang
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kumpulkan hingga jadi kenangan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kuhadapi sekarang
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mimpiku, posisiku
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.65,0:12:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Takkan kulepaskan lagi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suaraku, laguku
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari bernyanyi, la ta ta
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harapanku, panggungku
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kutunjukkan
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayapku, suaraku
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih tinggi-FLY HIGH
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang FLY HIGH
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menuju dunia baru bersama
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari lepas landas-FLY SO HIGH
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.67,0:12:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Lebih tinggi, lebih jauh
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rentangkan sayapmu, kita F/ACE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Terbang lebih tinggi dari sebelumnya
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terbang ke langit
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita F/ACE!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, semuanya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.21,0:13:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pesta penutupnya sudah mulai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kepalaku mau pecah,\Nterlalu banyak hal terjadi hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di situ kau rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Natsuki? Ngapain kau di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kulihat kau naik ke atap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kebetulan aku beres syuting di bawah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan itu maksudku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau ada yang lihat, bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua murid lagi di aula. Aman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.66,0:13:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah mulai dingin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kan makanan sisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.53,0:13:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bikin nostalgia saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi begini...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau dengar lagunya tadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.84,0:14:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bikin lagunya dengan bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waktu Kinoshita bilang kau buntu,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.26,0:14:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku khawatir banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagunya keren banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Khas kau banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.81,0:14:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, aku paling ingin\Nnyanyi lagu itu buatmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masih ingat, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku janji kalau kau lolos\Nkejuaraan nasional,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bakal nyanyi lagu ciptaanku buatmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kegagalan itu bukti kalau kau punya mimpi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan gampang menyerah.\NKumpulkan sedikit demi sedikit
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sampai jadi kenangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.83,0:14:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terbang lebih tinggi dari sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terbang ke langit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memang agak telat, sih,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan mimpimu mungkin sudah berubah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tetap saja, lagu ini kutulis\Nuntuk menyemangatimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.64,0:14:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan cuma buatmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi juga buat anak-anak di sekitarmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiba-tiba ngomong begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jadi lupa mau ngomong apa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.49,0:15:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau ceritakan semuanya.\NKau kayak orang mencurigakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana ada orang mencurigakan semanis aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf soal tempo hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dan juga,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}terima kasih sudah mendampingiku\Nselama ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah jadi penyanyi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baguslah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seandainya Tuan Suram\Nitu murid di sekolah kami,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa kami bisa bareng tiap hari?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.59,0:16:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka suruh kau kerja lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, aku yang mau.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sini kubantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benar-benar tak tahu malu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beraninya aku sandingkan namaku\Ndengan nama dewa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harusnya aku sadar diri!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Suram, kok di sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat kalau sampai ketahuan orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.87,0:16:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku langsung pergi, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cuma mau bilang terima kasih\Nsebelum pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah menemaniku\Nkeliling sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat menikmati\NFestival Budaya hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Festival Budaya kami\Nmemang cukup terkenal di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kubantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.73,0:17:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau rajin juga di sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tanganku gatal kalau tak ikut bersih-bersih.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf malah jadi merepotkanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak usah sungkan begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalau kau tak bertemu kami,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau pasti kumpul bareng teman-temanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.75,0:17:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku orang luar, tapi aku tak bisa\Nmembiarkanmu sendirian.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sebenarnya kerepotan, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak kusangka kau buang waktu\Nyang berharga ini
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}demi orang sepertiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benar-benar minta maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Biar aku lompat untuk menebus dosa!\N- Hei, jangan nekat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sifatnya kembali kayak di rumah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.59,0:17:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan anggap dirimu orang luar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.09,0:17:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga bersenang-senang, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau kan penggemarku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana mungkin kau tak senang?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon memang dewa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cuma itu yang mau kusampaikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:17:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, aku pamit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:18:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf sudah mengganggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau keren pakai kostum itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keren, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana, ya?\NSedikit di luar dugaan, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Suram.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.51,0:18:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lampunya nyala,\Ntapi tak ada orang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang lupa matikan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, biarlah, masa bodoh.\NAyo ke pesta penutupan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah kenapa,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}rasanya aku tak ingin\Ndia pulang sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.57,0:18:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada yang datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak sadar. Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi begini...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan karena kau biasku,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.67,0:18:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}atau karena kau idola.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada hubungannya dengan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.72,0:18:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi saat bersamamu,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku sangat bahagia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada perasaan tertentu\Nyang terpendam di hatiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beri aku waktu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.73,0:19:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi dari awal aku sudah ragu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.78,0:19:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudnya apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku harus jujur sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin tahu\Napa pendapatmu sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terhadapmu, aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pesta penutupannya sepertinya sudah selesai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak-anak bakal segera ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kembalilah ke Fujita sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai di sini dulu untuk hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.00,0:20:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada perasaan tertentu\Nyang terpendam di hatiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.90,0:20:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.41,0:20:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.54,0:20:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon, yang menyusutkan badan besarnya\Njadi seperti bola kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon, yang sangat perfeksionis\Nsoal detail sekecil apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tamon, yang berjuang keras\Ndemi impian besarnya
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan tersenyum konyol.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sifatnya murung, tapi warna\Nrambutnya mencolok. Aku suka itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga suka kebiasaannya menyentuh\Nhidung saat lagi malu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.65,0:21:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Walau terkadang\Ndia kelihatan agak seram,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tetap mencintainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sadar sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku benar-benar jatuh cinta padanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.09,0:21:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin ini sudah takdir
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.21,0:21:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sejak pertama kali aku menerkamnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.52,0:22:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Kinoshita. Bukankah ini hari liburmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.28,0:22:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berhenti...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.57,0:22:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi asisten rumah tangga.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.46,0:22:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak mau menjadi kehadiran\Nyang berbahaya bagi Tamon.
